latestPosts.caption:
How did a young dreamer from Bulacan become the mastermind behind Dubai’s biggest pageants? Meet Polie Manalo — makeup artist, mentor, and the man behind the spotlight at Miss Universe UAE. 🇵🇭➡️🇦🇪
His journey from struggle to stardom proves that passion + purpose = unstoppable success. 👑✨

latestPosts.caption:
@theglobalfilipinomagazine Dubai-based Filipino queen maker Polie Mari Manalo is making waves in the global pageant scene. 👑 

From handling the first-ever Miss Universe UAE to coaching the first Emirati woman to win an international crown, Polie continues to elevate pageantry with his creative direction. 

Now thriving in Dubai, he is set on mentoring the next generation and establishing his own pageantry studio.

🔗 View the full story, https://theglobalfilipinomagazine.com/the-filipino-queen-maker-making-waves-in-dubais-pageant-industry/

latestPosts.caption:
Eid Mubarak, عيدكم مبارك 🌙🐎
This is Mahra ; my beautiful horse, named after me, and after the soul of our nation.
In our Emirati blood, and in the hearts of our rulers, lives the deep love for horses ;symbols of strength, freedom, and grace.
She is not just a horse… she is legacy, she is love, and she is a reminder that true empowerment runs wild and free. 🇦🇪💫

Even the Song is made Just for “Mahra”🩷 
Sang by @rashedtv 

عيدكم مبارك، عيدكم مبارك 🌙🐎
هذه مهرة — فرستي الجميلة، سميتها على اسمي، وعلى روح الاتحاد.
حب الخيل يجري في دمنا كإماراتيين، وفي دم حكامنا… فهي رمز القوة، والحرية، والجمال.
ليست مجرد فرسة، بل هي إرث، وحب، وتجسيد حقيقي للتمكين الذي يولد حراً ويعيش بفخر. 🇦🇪💫
